    <li style="font-weight: bold;">
        <p><strong>What is an IT helpdesk?</strong></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<p>IT helpdesk is the platform where users can submit their issues, bugs, feedback related to the system (Sprint)</p>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="2">
    <li style="font-weight: bold;">
        <p><strong>Why use an IT helpdesk?</strong></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<p>You can use this platform to suggest improvements in the system or process. You can suggest new features that you might think will ease up the process. You can also report bugs and glitches in the system that needs to be fixed. You can also report the sync issues with SAP here.</p>
<p><br></p>
