        <p>What happens after you submit your request?</p>
    </li>
    <ol style="font-weight: initial;">
        <li>
            <p>Once we receive your request we sort them into categories as bugs, improvements and new feature requests. Sync issues and other glitches will be given the priority considering the urgency to streamline the operations.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>For the new feature requests, in the next step we present an initial solution with the requester and take feedback.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Design a solution. Take feedback from you. Test it with other users and finally implement the feature.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
    
</ol>
